%AI_Design_Template_for_Three_Side_Seal_Bag
%Package_Lab_Epackage_Design_Template
%Japanese_Market_Standard_Dimensions

Template_Name: 三方シール袋 (Three-Side Seal Bag)
Product_Category: flat_3_side
Standard_Sizes:
  - 100mm x 150mm
  - 120mm x 180mm
  - 150mm x 200mm
  - 200mm x 250mm

Design_Specifications:
  - Bleed: 3mm on all sides
  - Safety Zone: 5mm from edges
  - File Format: Adobe Illustrator CS6 or later
  - Color Mode: CMYK
  - Resolution: 300 DPI

Cutting_Guides:
  - Solid line: Final cut line
  - Dashed line: Crease line (if applicable)

Design_Elements:
  [Front_Panel]
  - Product logo area: Top center
  - Product name: Below logo
  - Product description: Center area
  - Weight/Volume: Bottom left
  - Barcode area: Bottom right
  - Nutrition info: Bottom panel (if applicable)

  [Back_Panel]
  - Ingredients list: Top area
  - Instructions: Center area
  - Manufacturer info: Bottom area
  - Expiry date: Bottom right

Color_Guidelines:
  - Primary colors: Brand specific
  - Text color: High contrast (minimum 60%)
  - Background: Consider transparency requirements

File_Naming_Convention:
  - Client_Project_ProductCode_Size.ai
  - Example: Epackage_Coffee_Brand_Flat3_100x150.ai

